I"õ<p>Comprimir</p>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">tar</span> <span class="nt">-czvf</span> directori.tar.gz directori
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Descomprimir</p>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">tar</span> <span class="nt">-xzvf</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Explicaci√≥</p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">-c</code>: Comprimeix</p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">-x</code>: Extrau, descomprimeix</p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">-z</code>: Gzip, utilitza aquesta algoritme</p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">-v</code>: Verbose, recurr√®ncia</p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">-f</code>: Fitxer, treballa amb aquest fitxer</p>

